UNUSED READY RUNNING READY
BLOCKED READY
ZOMBIE UNUSED

ol.li: Switch: context_switch() atomically swaps CPU state
Execution: Process runs until timer tick or yield
Exit: sys_exit() marks ZOMBIE, triggers reschedule

ul.li: TSS ESP0: Updated on every context switch
CR3 reload: Flushes TLB (unless global pages)

g.title: Array of 16 Process Control Blocks Each PCB: ~100 bytes Total: ~1.6KB
Circular doubly-linked list of READY processes
Function pointer array SYS_EXIT=0, SYS_WRITE=1, etc.
